- React is a JS Library not a Framework
- npx create-react-app [app-name] to create a react app;ication
- package.json contains details about all the dependecies required to run the application.
- functional components
  - a javascript functions
  - create a js file
  - then import react
  - then write a function
  - then export it.export default Greet.
  - example
  	import React from '.react'
	function Greet() {
		return <h1>Hello</h1>
	}
	export default Greet

